gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 132, Spurs 120
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Spurs, 132-120. Nikola Jokic recorded 39 points, 11 rebounds, and nine assists for the Nuggets, with Michael Porter Jr. adding 25 points and seven rebounds in the victory. Victor Wembanyama tallied 22 points, 11 rebounds, and six steals for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 11-6 in the regular season, while the Spurs fall to 3-14.
